# 📋 User Registration System - Manual Test Cases

This repository contains detailed manual test cases for a web-based **User Registration** module, focusing on functional, UI, and edge-case testing.

## 🔧 Modules Covered

- Registration Form
- Email Verification
- CAPTCHA
- Duplicate Account Prevention

## 🧪 Test Coverage Highlights

- Input Validation (Email, Password, Required Fields)
- Negative Test Scenarios
- UI/UX Layout and Label Checks
- Edge Case Handling (Long inputs, emojis, special chars)

## 📄 How to Use

- Navigate to `Registration_TestCases.xlsx` or view `TESTCASES.md` for a table format.
- Use these test cases to validate any typical user registration system.

